ParallelChunk.en:
I have received no requests for amendments to the agenda for Monday, Tuesday or Wednesday; 
          however
        , Mr McMillan-Scott has asked to be allowed to speak.

By way of clarification, the intention is that black boxes will be incorporated in new goods ships as from 1 July 2002; 
          and
         that for existing goods ships, in the case of those of 20 000 tonnes gross or more, this will apply from 1 January 2007 and for those of between 3 000 and 20 000 tonnes, from 1 January 2008.

ParallelChunk.fr:
